This site is titled:<br><br>
Re:Vietnam<br>
*Stories After the War*<br><br>
In that regard, free swing of thoughts, positions, and ideas *are* appropriate. Many aspects of the Vietnam War strongly influence the positions that many Vietnam Veterans take today on wide ranging contemporary social, political, and military issues. Their issues are all connected in their mind, and have validity from their point of view. These things command as much respect as the thoughts and feelings of those who are not so endowed with the trauma of the Vietnam experience.<br><br>
I am a Vietnam Veteran, I have thoughts, feelings, positions that are influenced by my past experience. I will not deny them. They must not be denied in others.
